This AWP is planned to formulate a project preparation grant in order to design for a full size project implementation in next year.
 The total budget for PPG is $ 120,000.

project_descr: Strengthening Community Resilience to Climate Induced Natural Disasters in the Dili to Ainaro Road Development Corridor, Timor Leste
project_title: GEF 5108 LDCF PPG: Strengthening Community Resilience
